asset.hookText: Hi Lee. We saw your review on Amazon. The FloorMate Deluxe should pick up exceptionally well. We had a few tips to get it working properly. Felicia put together a video for you to get it working. Sorry to hear you spilled some solution as well. If you can, send us an e-mail at andy.netzel@ttifloorcare.com. Thanks again for your thoughtful review, and let us know if you need anything else. We're here for you.
